Man I was in a miserable funk last night in that 3rd qtr. You can read my tweets and see. I was irate. However, when Johnson ran back out...
•Morrow needs to give Gran a swirly for dialing up quick three and outs that the D had 70+ snaps and almost 40 game minutes on the field.
•The defense made plays when it had to. TFL’s and QB sacks happened at many key times UK needed a play.
•For a second time this season, Barker ended all questions about him not playing. Bowden gave better QB play in one pass. He should transfer
•Another game that I am really not sure CJ Conrad even dressed.
•The game changed when Johnson came back out from that locker room. He finally played to win a game instead of not to lose one.
•Benny found a new gear last night. That run where he bashed the UT defender’s head repeatedly as he ran to the sideline was manly.
•I do credit the D in bailing out the offense, only allowing 9 points that should have been at least 21. Helped negate a -4 TO margin.
•If you play against UK, and don’t take advantage of the soft coverage to pick up easy 5-7 yard gains, you deserve to lose. It’s always open
•I do not trust our coaching staff. At all. Gran is 0-7 on calling a late 2nd-3rd quarter game. The run was working, why all the passes?
